snippet.title: Future Spy [Arcade Longplay] (1984) Sega {315-5061}
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Future Spy. released back in 1984 by Sega. Based on Zaxxon hardware. The game has the same isometric view like Zaxxon.
